        # Informant

        Traditional analytics track traffic, not usability - Informant tells you when your users trigger form errors, so you know where they're getting tripped up. It's the brainchild of myself and [Paul Elliott](https://twitter.com/p_elliott), and is currently a Heroku addon, with many exciting features & additions imminent.

        I'm the cofounder of Informant, LLC, and handle branding and all design, branding, and UI/UX concerns. You should install Informant. Trust me.

        [visit informantapp.com](http://www.informantapp.com)

