        # Hotel Insider

        Hotel Insider is a boutique hotel reservation system catering to more exclusive clientele. Hashrocket was contracted to custom-build the internal administration system, from booking & hotel publishing workflows down to basic content management.

        I worked within the (very nice) Hotel Insider branding guidelines and handled UI/UX, design, HAML, SASS and a chunk or two of Javascript.

