        # Fanhub

        Fanhub is a CRM tool for medium-sized businesses. Features include a ticket tracking system, sales pipeline, and client/company management all built around a sophisticated "card stack" UI paradigm.

        The desktop web app is complimented by an iPhone app, developed in-house at Hashrocket. I handled branding, design, and UI for all of the above, and also handled a full look & feel update of the web & mobile apps to a flat iOS 7 aesthetic.

